{"tid":1193990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方拒絕開放石地足球場予集會市民，指不是警方責任 應找維園經理","createTime":"2019-06-09T06:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T07:52:34.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a63467177ca84063fb342cde7eab3d97aa89d3","tid":1193990,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】民陣下午發起反對修訂逃犯條例遊行。<br />\n<br />\n民陣不滿警方拒絕開放石地足球場讓市民集合，擔心會引起混亂。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線召集人岑子杰：「硬地足球場有兩個在維修，有四個沒有人使用，在曬太陽，民陣很擔心如果有市民見到那兒是空地自行在那裏集合，維園如何安排出發呢？一個音響都沒有設置，我們應否事先與警方達成共識，避免屆時有爭拗。可惜維園的經理失蹤，警方指不是警方責任，因為這裏是維園場地，要求主辦單位自己想辦法。」"},{"pid":"2b13bec3b1259a7ea84842729d845320ba1986f3","tid":1193990,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2915a2654584b5b838480db201c34820c39ed90c","tid":1193990,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"咁政總呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12fb84ffd1517acdf69c4406c6add52c92efe5f","tid":1193990,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ed9f8f8aee366140ab7dc040f40ba6ff6f0a30","tid":1193990,"uid":19055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"黑警責任係欺壓市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6810633584250f88c4c8610297e1b7dc3b0a6f1","tid":1193990,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"街場踢波都唔畀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a95cecf05191c751dacf54d4f53eb6bbee352e","tid":1193990,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T07:03:24.000Z","msg":"點解六四果陣又開？"},{"pid":"ae475ec5dd1